    <h2>Experiments</h2>

    <div class = "clean">

    <p class = "list"> Several experiments were conducted to find out more about pet microbe #705. Each experiment revealed
        some information about the given microbe. They included experiments on how #705 reacted to tempature change,
        along with its interactions with other microbes and living organisms. Data gathered from these
        experiments allowed me to determine what type of microbe it was.
      </br>
      </br>
      <strong>A total of 4 experiments were conducted:</strong>
    </p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong><a href='exp1'>Experiment 1</a></strong>: The effect of temperature on Microbe #705.</li>
      <li><strong><a href='exp2'>Experiment 2</a></strong>: How does Microbe #705 interact with Microbe #206?  </li>
      <li><strong><a href='exp3'>Experiment 3</a></strong>: How does Microbe #705 interact with a hornworms?</li>
      <li><strong><a href='exp4'>Experiment 4</a></strong>: How does Microbe #705 interact with pea seed germination? </li>
    </ul>
